ith `0/0` calls.\n\n1. On the preserved branch, fix or reproduce the `native-image-agent` environment problem for `generateMetadata` so the agent library is available to the test JVM.\n2. Re-run metadata/stats generation for `org.tpolecat:skunk-core_3:1.1.0-RC1` and confirm that `metadata/.../1.1.0-RC1/reachability-metadata.json` and `stats/.../1.1.0-RC1/stats.json` are actually emitted with non-empty dynamic-access results.\n3. If that succeeds, review whether the added `-H:+AllowDeprecatedBuilderClassesOnImageClasspath` workaround in the preserved branch is acceptable for this library or needs a cleaner follow-up."}}
